text: The Parliament of Eswatini (Swazi: Libandla) is the large group of legislators, or lawmakers, of the country of Eswatini. It is made of two groups called "chambers". These chambers are: *The Senate, or Upper Chamber *The House of Assembly or Lower Chamber. Both groups are located in Lobamba. == Related pages == * Parliamentary procedure * Legislatures == Other websites == * Eswatini Eswatini Category:Eswatini Category:Government in Africa
